title: Centro Cultural Matienzo
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Matienzo is a cultural center with a venue and an active music, art, and theatre program. There is a bar and terrace on the ground floor where meals, snacks, and alcohol is served. Menu indicates the vegetarian options - need to ask staff which ones are vegan suitable. Items include pizza, wok stir fry, veggie burger, empanadas, sandwiches, hummus, guacamole, nachos.
